task.summary:
- Implemented BandpassFilterBank class - basic FIR filter - test_bandpass contains unit tests
- Implemented PlotAudio class - plots FFT - plots Waveform - plots Filter response
- Implemented spectrum_loudness.py frontent - Added filter_bank methoed to BandpassFilterBank - Added filter_bank unit test
- Implemented spectral_loudness.audio.engine - Added Engine class which loops wav file - Added filter_bank Engine.run
- Dynamic Range Measurement now functioning though results are incorrect.
Added an array of fifo's to manage each frequency band
- changed FIFO to 3d numpy array - fixed bandpass corner freq bug - changed dynamic range output to mono
- moved decimation to follow all filtering
- refactored to merge stereo files before filter + measurements
- refactored engine and loudness to run in realtime with audio playback - dynamic range values are now written to the given output path
